{
  "stem": "8252.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was planning to go back to Poland and, you know, this was our home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We wouldn't have found ourselves in, in this wonderful country.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was-- I was in charge of one 75-millimeter gun and the crew of the gun.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Front line, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they asked me-- they asked me whether I want to go-- because of my education, they asked me whether I want to go to officer's school.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I refused.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wanted to go to the front.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, somehow or other I feel that I made all the right choices.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know it at the time, but I made all the right choices because I am here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, you know, my, my helmet was shot, you know, had a big hole in it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My jacket was shot at and had big holes in it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was under, under artillery barrage many times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was under artillery barrage when I volunteered to unload a truck of ammunition.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, you know, I volunteered because I was-- I was single.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So only my parents would cry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were some guys who had wives and children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Poles know their Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Poles know their Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's one reason that I had to be a much better soldier than anybody else because I had to show them that Jews can be good soldiers.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, that's why I have been rewarded with Polish Cross of Valor and French Croix de Guerre, you know, at the battlefield.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was promoted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I had to show that I'm better soldier than anybody else although I am a Jew, although I am the pariah.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, whether it was conscious or not conscious or just below the consciousness.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
